text: Choguel Kokalla Maïga (born 1958) is a Malian politician. He is President of the Patriotic Movement for Renewal. In June 2021, he became the Prime Minister of Mali."Mali : Assimi Goïta Président, Dr Choguel Maïga Premier ministre", Afrik.com, 29 May 2021 . ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Mali
title: Choguel Kokalla Maïga
